<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ChopSign 验证码</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap');
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans Sc', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #2c3e50;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #f5f7fa;
    }
    
    .container {
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    
    .code-container {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f0f4ff, #e6f0ff);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 28px 0;
    }
    
    .verification-code {
      font-size: 38px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      color: #3867d6;
      text-align: center;
      text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    p {
      color: #4a5568;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    
    .highlight {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #3867d6;
    }
    
    .footer {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #a0aec0;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 28px;
      padding-top: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid #edf2f7;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <p>您好：</p>
    <p>您正在请求登录您的<span class="highlight">筷签账号</span>，您的登录验证码为：</p>
    <div class="code-container">
      <div class="verification-code">{{ code }}</div>
    </div>
    <p>验证码有效期为 <span class="highlight">{{ expiresIn }} 分钟</span>。</p>
    <p>请勿将验证码泄露给他人，以确保账号安全</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>感谢您使用筷签账号。</p>
      <p>© {{ year }} ChopSign · 版权所有</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>